txt.en: 'Wha? Huh? Another book? How many of these books are there? For goodness sake, I'm never going to get any sleep!\n\n'Well let's get this over with. Speak to me again if you want to complete Book XI.'
'Book XI completion coming right up! Now leave me be!'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book XI of the Epic quest series.
